== 地理==

安塔基亞坐落於[[奧龍特斯河|奧龍特斯河]]邊，離[[地中海|地中海]]約{{convert|22|km|mi}}。環城皆山，北部為[[努爾山脈|努爾山脈]]、東部Keldağ山，為南部為Jebel Akra。盛產[[大理石|大理石]]。同時因為坐落於[[死海斷層|死海斷層]]北部邊緣，故易受地震威脅。

城東北部的平原受奧龍特斯河、[[卡拉蘇河_(哈塔伊省)|卡拉蘇河]]和[[阿夫林河|阿夫林河]]灌溉而特別肥沃，平原上本有一湖，1980年被一家法國公司排乾了。同時又興建了貫穿城中心的運河。<ref>Avotaynu: the international review of Jewish genealogy, Volume 14, G. Mokotoff, 1998, [http://books.google.com/books?id=77RtAAAAMAAJ&q=Information+comes+from+the+Jewish+communities+of+Antakya+Bodrum+Bursa+Canakkale+Corlu+Edirne+Finike+Gelibolu+Iskendorun+Istanbul+Izmir+Kilis+Kirklarelli+Manisa+and+Tire+plus+a+few+scattered+stones+from+other+Gazi-Antep&dq=Information+comes+from+the+Jewish+communities+of+Antakya+Bodrum+Bursa+Canakkale+Corlu+Edirne+Finike+Gelibolu+Iskendorun+Istanbul+Izmir+Kilis+Kirklarelli+Manisa+and+Tire+plus+a+few+scattered+stones+from+other+Gazi-Antep&hl=en&ei=fbSJTo7lNe7zmAWQyegX&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA p. 40.] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=77RtAAAAMAAJ&q=Information+comes+from+the+Jewish+communities+of+Antakya+Bodrum+Bursa+Canakkale+Corlu+Edirne+Finike+Gelibolu+Iskendorun+Istanbul+Izmir+Kilis+Kirklarelli+Manisa+and+Tire+plus+a+few+scattered+stones+from+other+Gazi-Antep&dq=Information+comes+from+the+Jewish+communities+of+Antakya+Bodrum+Bursa+Canakkale+Corlu+Edirne+Finike+Gelibolu+Iskendorun+Istanbul+Izmir+Kilis+Kirklarelli+Manisa+and+Tire+plus+a+few+scattered+stones+from+other+Gazi-Antep&hl=en&ei=fbSJTo7lNe7zmAWQyegX&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA |date=20200727150948 }}</ref>

